data.description: *MOTIVATED SELLERS- OFFERING $7,000 CREDIT WITH ACCEPTED OFFER!* Welcome to your Haughton hideaway! This large, stunning home offers a luxurious and spacious retreat in a secluded neighborhood. Boasting a massive primary suite that exudes comfort & style, this property is perfect for those who crave a serene and spacious sanctuary. With a generous living area that invites relaxation and entertainment, a screened in sunroom, and an outdoor pavilion, this home is an entertainer's paradise. Step outside to your very own inground gunite pool where you can bask in the sun and take a refreshing dip on warm summer days. The expansive tree-studded lot provides shade, privacy, and a picturesque backdrop that adds to the charm of this exceptional property. With a newer roof, updated appliances, newer downstairs HVAC and hot water heater, this home can help ease homeowner worries. Enjoy great schools and convenience to town with this ultimate escape from the hustle & bustle of daily life.
